all constructive criticism would be appreciated. --Dethe (Tom Martin)
 Bugs and changes send to Palio@blinksoft.com
 Original Author Dethe e-mail:  tmartin@st6000.sct.edu"


%rooms
/* -------------------------- GROUNDS ------------------------------- */

		manse_rd1

title "The Gate to the Wizard's Mansion"
descr
"       You halt before the towering steel gates blocking entry into the
Mansion of Tobas the Wizard of Telven. The gates are made of smooth polished
steel, and swing inwards. The north road lies behind you to the west. A
small sign is posted here."
extra {"sign"}
"The Wizard's Mansion is for players levels 7-10."
movement SECT_FIELD
west to north_rd6@moor;
east to manse_rd5
	open {EX_OPEN_CLOSE, EX_CLOSED}
	keyword {"steel gate", "gate"}
	descr "The steel gate effectively halts all traffic in and out.";
ALWAYS_LIGHT
end

		manse_rd2

title "Wall Road"
descr
"       You stand at the base of the Mansion's north-west wall tower.
The tower appears to be made from millions of tiny rocks, and has no visible
entrance. Wall Road continues to the east and south."
movement SECT_CITY
east to manse_rd9;
south to manse_rd3;
end

		manse_rd3

title "Wall Road"
descr
"       You stand on Wall Road, the shadows of the Mansion's wall falling
over you. Wall Road continues to the north and south from this point."
movement SECT_CITY
north to manse_rd2;
south to manse_rd4;
end

		manse_rd4

title "Wall Road"
descr
"       You stand on Wall Road, the shadows of the Mansion's wall falling
over you. Wall Road continues to the north, and south to the Wizard's Walk."
movement SECT_CITY
north to manse_rd3;
south to manse_rd5;
end

		manse_rd5

title "The End of the Wizard's Walk"
descr
"       You stand at the end of the Wizard's Walk. The walk appears to
stretch off in the distance to the east. To the west are the Mansion's gates.
To the north and south, a road follows beside the Mansion's wall."
movement SECT_CITY
north to manse_rd4;
south to manse_rd6;
east to manse_rd10;
west to manse_rd1
	open {EX_OPEN_CLOSE, EX_CLOSED}
	keyword {"steel gate", "gate"}
	descr "The large steel gates block passage to and from the Mansion.";
ALWAYS_LIGHT
end

		manse_rd6

title "Wall Road"
descr
"       You stand on Wall Road, the shadows of the Mansion's wall falling
over you. Wall road continues to the south, and north to the Wizard's Walk."
movement SECT_CITY
north to manse_rd5;
south to manse_rd7;
end

		manse_rd7

title "Wall Road"
descr
"       You stand on Wall Road, the shadows of the Mansion's wall falling
