		manse_rd8

title "Wall Road"
descr
"       You stand at the base of the Mansion's south-west wall tower.
The tower appears to be made from millions of tiny rocks, and has no visible
entrance. Wall Road continues to the east and north."
movement SECT_CITY
north to manse_rd7;
east to manse_rd11;
end

		manse_rd9

title "Behind the Wizard's Stables"
descr
"       As you step behind the Wizard's grand stables, the shadows deepen.
An acrid smell is present in the air. Sniffing more carefully brings back
your own memories of your first experience with Old Firebreather. Scanning
the ground you see the discheveled remains of a game of craps."
movement SECT_CITY
west to manse_rd2;
end

		manse_rd10

title "Along the Wizard's Walk"
descr
"        You find yourself travelling along the Wizard's Walk.  The air here
is fresh and clean. A gentle breeze blows leaves on the Walk. Life is GOOD."
movement SECT_CITY
east to manse_rd13;
west to manse_rd5;
ALWAYS_LIGHT
end

		manse_rd11

title "Behind the Supply House"
descr
"       Walking behind the Mansion's supply house you wander into the
deepening shadows. The growing darkness send a sense of dread through your
body. The ground here is torn up in great rents, as though a battle has
recently taken place here."
movement SECT_CITY
west to manse_rd8;
end

		manse_rd12

title "Entrance to the Mansion's Grand Stables"
descr
"       You stand at the entrance to the Mansion's grand stables. The smell
of hay and manure emanate from the door to the north. The stables resemble
those described in a fairy tale you can almost remember from your early
youth. A feeling of unease passes through you as you remember the details of
the stables residents."
movement SECT_CITY
south to manse_rd13;
north to stable_rd4
	open {EX_OPEN_CLOSE, EX_CLOSED}
	keyword {"stable door", "door"}
	descr "The door is painted white with a centered black pentagram.";
end

		manse_rd13

title "Wizard's Cross Walk"
descr
"    You stand at the cross roads of the Wizard's Walk. The Walk continues
in the four compass direction at this location. To the north, you can hear
the faint sounds of angry hooves. To the south you see the outline of the
Mansion's Supply House. The Wizard's Walk continues to the east and west."
movement SECT_CITY
north to manse_rd12;
south to manse_rd14;
east to manse_rd15;
west to manse_rd10;
ALWAYS_LIGHT
end

		manse_rd14

title "Entrance to the Mansion's Supply House"
descr
"       You stand before the entrance of the Mansion's supply house. The
house stands in perfect condition, as though it has never been used. The
path leading up to its door is still covered by grass."
movement SECT_CITY
north to manse_rd13;
south to supply_rd3
	open {EX_OPEN_CLOSE, EX_CLOSED}
	keyword {"supply door", "door"};
end

		manse_rd15

title "The End of the Wizard's Walk"
descr
"       At this end of the Wizard's Walk, you stand before the Wizard's
Mansion itself. The Mansion looms above you three stories into the sky. The
double doors to the east lead into the Mansion itself."
extra {"double door", "door"}
"The doors are made of diamond, and seem to glow with a light of their own.
"
movement SECT_CITY
west to manse_rd13;
east to hall_rd1
	open {EX_OPEN_CLOSE, EX_CLOSED}
	keyword {"double door", "door"};
ALWAYS_LIGHT
end

