descr
"       You are inside a horse stall. This is where Tobas the Wizard keeps
his famous Demon Horses. Judging from the scratches and dents in the walls,
Tobas is the one of the two who prefers them to stay here. The door is east
and the stable extends to the south. A large pile of hay, manure, and
assorted muck is in one corner."
movement SECT_FIELD
south to stable_rd2;
east to stable_rd4
	open {EX_OPEN_CLOSE, EX_CLOSED}
	keyword {"door"};
end

