/* ----------------------------- GUILD -------------------------------- */

		garden_rd1

title "An Underground Garden"
descr
"The garden you see before you contains plants that time has forgotten. The
beauty of the flowers and plants is heart-stopping. Although the beauty here
is great, it is obvious that this area is frequented by a small number of
people. One of the possibly residing under the grounds here. However, you
feel that it would be foolish to assume they are mere caretakers, and
nothing more."
movement SECT_CITY
flags {UNIT_FL_NO_WEATHER}
up to maze_rd17;
north to garden_rd3;
west to garden_rd2;
down to garden_rd5;
east to garden_rd4;
ALWAYS_LIGHT
end

		garden_rd2

title "The Western End"
descr
"This is the western end of the underground gardens. The gardens here make
you feel as if you hare full of life. Your senses come alive, and you smell
the sweet essence of the surrounding flowers. This is definately a place of
good and healing."
movement SECT_CITY
flags {UNIT_FL_NO_WEATHER}
east to garden_rd1;
ALWAYS_LIGHT
flags {UNIT_FL_SACRED}
end

		garden_rd3

title "The Northern End"
descr
"This is the northern end of the underground gardens. The gardens here make
you feel the forces of growth. If you had the choice, this would be the spot
in all the lands you would come to enhance your innate abilities."
movement SECT_CITY
flags {UNIT_FL_NO_WEATHER}
south to garden_rd1;
ALWAYS_LIGHT
end

		garden_rd4

title "The Eastern End"
descr
"This is the eastern end of the underground gardens. This area of the gardens
is cast in shadows. A sense of dread fills the air, and causes the hairs on
the back of your neck to stand on end. This is definately a place of evil and
dark powers."
movement SECT_CITY
flags {UNIT_FL_NO_WEATHER}
west to garden_rd1;
ALWAYS_LIGHT
end

		garden_rd5

title "Temple of the Body"
descr "You see what you are. And what you are, determines what you see."
movement SECT_CITY
flags {UNIT_FL_NO_WEATHER}
up to garden_rd1;
ALWAYS_LIGHT
end


